author: Sanaa Shah
title: Alia Bhatt & Mahira Khan Wore The Exact Same Outfit
text:
Sanaa Shah Mar . 27 . 2017 Are we seeing double? Mahira Khan Mahira Khan 
We spotted Mahira Khan a couple of months ago in an all-white ensemble looking ethereal. She was styled by celebrity stylist Ami Patel for the promotions of Raees . While Mahira wore this look back in Jan, we spotted Alia wearing the EXACT same outfit a couple of days ago for the Youtube fest. Alia Bhatt A post shared by Alia ✨⭐️ (@aliaabhatt) on Mar 24, 2017 at 8:11am PDT 
Alia was styled by celebrity stylist Lakshmi Lehr in silver heels just like Mahira did back in Jan this year. While both of them perfected this look in the most co-ordinated way, we’re wondering if Lakshmi was aware that the exact same look was already worn by Mahira. 
Nonetheless, lucky for us cause there’s nothing wrong in seeing double. Are you have a problem with them twining? Let us know by commenting below. 0 TAGS
